  "dialogue": {
    "10": {
      "id": "10",
      "speaker": "Boss Friol",
      "text": "You made it out of the sewers, I see. Cool your heels a moment, and let's talk.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "LOW_MinscHideout_RoahBribe_ZhentLeaderSawUs",
        "LOW_Guildhall_State_DuringCoup"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "31",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "7": {
          "id": "7",
          "speaker": "Boss Friol",
          "text": "Nine-Fingers is done. My Zhentarim stand ready to purge this place of everyone loyal to her.",
          "context": "",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "31",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "22": {
              "id": "22",
              "speaker": "Boss Friol",
              "text": "So all I need to know is - does that include you, or not?",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "31",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "26": {
                  "id": "26",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Why are the Zhentarim working for the cult? They want everyone dead.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "31",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "4": {
                      "id": "4",
                      "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                      "text": "Aye, not ideal. But we don't plan on going along with that - only on taking the opportunity this whole situation offers.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "6": {
                          "id": "6",
                          "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                          "text": "The Zhentarim have been trying to crack Baldur's Gate for years, but Nine-Fingers' grip has been too strong. And look what it's come to.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "41": {
                              "id": "41",
                              "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                              "text": "Her Guild is disorganised. Undisciplined. The cult broke them in a matter of days, while my Zhentarim still stand strong.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "15": {
                                  "id": "15",
                                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                  "text": "A Guild under our control can do what Nine-Fingers failed to - drive the Absolute out of the city, once and for all.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "29": {
                                      "id": "29",
                                      "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                      "text": "I've seen enough to know you want the Absolute booted out of the city - same as I do. No reason we can't work together.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "35": {
                                          "id": "35",
                                          "speaker": "Player",
                                          "text": "Enough talking. Get out of my way, or die.",
                                          "context": "",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "40": {
                                              "id": "40",
                                              "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                              "text": "You don't know good sense when you hear it. But fine - have it your way.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "5": {
                                                  "id": "5",
                                                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                                  "text": "Zhentarim! Anyone who isn't us, dies!",
                                                  "context": "NodeContext: Shouting to her troops to launch an attack",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [
                                                    "LOW_Guildhall_Event_PickSideGuild"
                                                  ],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
