          "children": {
            "9": {
              "id": "9",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "What now?",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "11",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "19": {
                  "id": "19",
                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                  "text": "New coat of paint, I think. Then we introduce ourselves to the local vermin - let them know there's been a change of management.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "11",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {}
                }
              }
            },
            "3": {
              "id": "3",
              "speaker": "Player",
              "text": "I'm still not entirely clear what I get out of this deal.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "25",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "18": {
                  "id": "18",
                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                  "text": "Besides that dragon's hoard you got from the Counting House?",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "25",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "11": {
                      "id": "11",
                      "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                      "text": "But don't worry. We'll be at your back when it comes time to boot the Absolute out.",
                      "context": "NodeContext: 'Sword captain' is a reference to herself - a faux-humble 'yours truly', as she's sure she'll get a promotion",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [
                        "LOW_Guildhall_State_ZhentWillHelpEND"
                      ],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "25",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "16": {
                          "id": "16",
                          "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                          "text": "Might be I'll even be flaunting a shiny new rank. I just handed my superiors quite the catch.",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "25",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "2": {
                              "id": "2",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "I did.",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "25",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "1": {
                                  "id": "1",
                                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                  "text": "Aye, and I'm grateful. Baldur's Gate was the last city along the coast that we hadn't quite put our bootprint on.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "25": {
                                      "id": "25",
                                      "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                      "text": "We're here to stay, now. And when the battle-horns start blowing, you'll see we're as good as our word.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "17": {
                                          "id": "17",
                                          "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                          "text": "Most of the time.",
                                          "context": "NodeContext: Faux-formality, with a little bow. She does mean it, but she's toying with us a little bit - we've just seen firsthand that she has no problem going back on her word.",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "",
                                          "is_end": true,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {}
                                        }
                                      }
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "46": {
                              "id": "46",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "And you only had to collaborate with a death-cult to do it. Your superiors won't mind?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "25",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "24": {
                                  "id": "24",
                                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                  "text": "Hah. They all did the same or worse - that's how they got to be my superiors.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "25",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {}
                                }
                              }
                            },
                            "21": {
                              "id": "21",
                              "speaker": "Player",
                              "text": "Why does the Zhentarim care so much about Baldur's Gate?",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "17",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "30": {
                                  "id": "30",
                                  "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                  "text": "Simple enough - because it wasn't ours. Couldn't be, so long as Nine-Fingers was around.",
                                  "context": "",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "17",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "34": {
                                      "id": "34",
                                      "speaker": "Boss Friol",
                                      "text": "Now the Guild can become a Zhent operation - and we'll have your back when the battle-horns start blowing. I'm as good as my word.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [],
                                      "ruletags": [],
